@startuml
title Kiến trúc Client-Server 3 lớp (3-Tier / Layered Architecture)

[Frontend\n(frontend-user + frontend-admin)] as FE
note right of FE : Tier 1: Presentation\n2 SPA (React + TS + Vite)

[Backend API\n(Express.js)\nRoutes → Controllers → (Services) → Models] as BACKEND
note right of BACKEND : Tier 2: Application / Logic

database "PostgreSQL\n(Supabase)" as DB
note right of DB : Tier 3: Data

FE --> BACKEND : REST API (JSON, JWT, HTTPS)
BACKEND --> DB : SQL có tham số hoá (pg, không ORM)

@enduml
